@node history "History"

This is third program in "Guide to the" series. This serie has now
expanded from football to contain Formula One too. Look out for
the other two projects already in the Aminet:

Directory->(docs/misc)

WorldCup.lha      ->       Guide to the World Cup
EuroChamp.lha     ->       Guide to the European Championships

